    "\", p.1283 12 Havemann, Negra [115] Origination & issuance Deposits & loans \"Alternative strategies include financial derivatives1 and CAT bonds as well as new forms of more decentralized finance such as security token offerings (STOs) and crowdfunding.",
    "\", p. 1283 13 Howson [116] Deposits & loans \"The evolution of decentralized finance systems (or DeFi), which use cryptocurrencies to package together collateralized debt products, is rapidly creating new risks for nonprofits who engage them as a revenue stream.",
    "\", p.817 14 Huang, Vismara [117] Origination & issuance Deposits & loans \"Compared with other fundraising markets such as IPOs, peer-to-peer lending, and equity crowdfunding, an ICO-as blockchain-based decentralized finance-has limitations and challenges (Martino et al., 2019a, 2019b).",
    "Since the market and regulatory bodies are not yet mature, the ICO market is relatively vulnerable to scammers and frauds (Cumming et al., 2015)\", p.4 15 Hughes [15] Origination & issuance Deposits & loans \"DeFi is a broad term that refers to decentralized finance generally.",
    "It can include issuances that are designed to be decentralized despite using a permissioned ledger, along with truly decentralized issuances on public blockchains."
